# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Notes
# ------------------------------------------------------------
#
# - This module contains NO backend logic itself.
# - It only aggregates and exposes backend entry points.
# - Backend implementations (LLVM, Cranelift, GCC, etc.)
#   must live behind `codegen.vit`.
# - Linking policy is centralized in `link.vit`.
#
# - This layout allows:
#     * multiple codegen backends
#     * cross-compilation
#     * LTO and post-link passes
